description: How long are we going to live like this? How long are we going to allow our economy to be destroyed through government-mandated job losses? How long are we going to scare people into wearing masks that restrict the oxygen flow to their brains? I MEAN COME ON. This is NOT about our safety or wellbeing. I’m so done with all of this. #corona #coronavirus #death #flu #life #covid #covid19 #sham #tryanny
